creator: Virtuagym Professional
descriptionHtml:
Begin your journey to a healthier lifestyle and let RD MAX HEALTH HUB help you along the way. Introducing RD Max, the most comprehensive fitness platform from Raindrop Enterprises. We are here to TRAIN YOU FOR LIFE, NOT JUST A SEASON!

PLEASE NOTE: YOU NEED AN RD Max ACCOUNT TO ACCESS THIS APP. IF YOU'RE A MEMBER GET IT FOR FREE FROM YOUR COACH OR TRAINER OR BY VISITING US AT RAINDROP ENTERPRISES, LLC


*Check class and event schedules and book your reservations

*Misc tracking and registration forms

*Beginner, Intermediate, Advanced fitness and activity levels

*Customizable and personalized meal plans

*Meal and Food Tracker

*Barcode Scanner for food and product recognition

*Globally track and convert units of measure where ever you are

*Medical and RX tracking information and reminders

*Introduces key personal organizational and priority tips and systems to help you with your busy
daily schedule and demands on your time.

*Includes a customizable calendar for easy planning and better time management

*Implements a Return and Report system that is vital in changing and sustaining your lifestyle

*Promotes outdoor activities as well as tips for better athletic performance

*Track your daily fitness, nutrition and sleep activities

*Track your weight and other key body composition, chemistry and metrics's

*Over 2000+ exercises and activities

*Clear 3D exercise demonstrations

*Personalized video demonstrations for viewing before and after your event or workout

*Preset workouts and meal plans with the option to create your own

*Over 150 badges to earn along with other motivating reward programs


Select from the various activities, programs, workouts and classes on or offline. Synchronize them with your app to track your progress while at home, during workouts, on the trail, shopping or in the gym. From fitness to nutrition to sleep, this app works along with your personal trainer, physical therapist or coach giving you the tools and motivation you need to create and maintain a health life style for a greater quality of life!

Select from the various activities, programs, workouts and classes on or offline. Synchronize them with your app to track your progress while at home, during workouts, on the trail, shopping or in the gym.
